Saksh whatsapp business client is a plateform that allows your communicate with your customer and provide whatsapp chat support to your customers who connect with whatsapp number. Using single admin panel you can manage unlimited whatsapp business numbers and connect with many meta applications. You can also connect with the OPAN AI for automatic answers. You can also schedule a message to all your customers it will be efective deliver on time.

