Features

1 Unlimited meta app configurartion
2 Unlimited whatsapp account
3 Schedule whatsapp message 
4 Custom API for 3rd party application integration
5 Export Chat to email 
6 Block Customer / Ban customer
7 Bookmark a message and filter by bookmark
8 Google Recaptcha v3 integrated
9 Admin Login history in admin for security audit and email notification on each login.
10 Script autobackup and configurable by admin 
 
 
 What are the benenfis of purchasing our application
 
 1 Save your time 
 -- You can provide whatsapp support from our custom build laravel based application and handle many  customers same time.
 
 2 Save subscription fee
 -- For whatsapp API / panel we uses wati like plateform but using this you don't need any of these and thus Save subscription fee.
 
 3 Grow your business.
 -- With direct whatsapp support you can grow customers trust and thus business.
 
 4 Marketing messages
 -- You can schedule marketing message and send your customers fully automatic once set and do other job it will handle everything.
 
 






